flowchart TD
    Start[Node Heartbeat Triggers Scheduler] --> Traverse{Start at root Queue}
    Traverse --> CheckChildQueues[Sort child queues by Capacity/Fairness metric]
    CheckChildQueues --> ChooseChild[Select queue furthest below capacity/share]
    ChooseChild --> IsLeaf{Is Leaf Queue?}
    IsLeaf -- No --> Traverse
    IsLeaf -- Yes --> CheckUserLimits{Does user exceed limit?}
    CheckUserLimits -- Yes --> SkipQueue[Skip Queue/App and evaluate next]
    CheckUserLimits -- No --> SortApps[Sort applications in Leaf Queue]
    SortApps --> CheckLocality{Evaluate app's resource requests against Node's locality}
    CheckLocality -- Node-Local Match --> Allocate[Allocate Node-Local Container]
    CheckLocality -- Rack-Local Match --> Allocate
    CheckLocality -- No Match --> HoldOrOffSwitch{Locality Delay Active?}
    HoldOrOffSwitch -- Yes --> SkipApp[Skip app to wait for locality Match]
    HoldOrOffSwitch -- No --> AllocateOff[Allocate Off-Switch Container]
    Allocate --> UpdateUsage[Update Queue & User Usage Metrics]
    AllocateOff --> UpdateUsage
    UpdateUsage --> End[Return Container Token in Heartbeat response]
